TI  - Problems and countermeasures of cage culture in Guizhou province.
T2  - Guizhou Agricultural Sciences
M3  - Journal article
AB  - Problems of cages culture in Guizhou province were analyzed aiming at the current situation of cage culture. Countermeasures to promote cage culture development in Guizhou province were proposed from aspects of rationally planning farming area, extending non-bait fish farming skills, selecting good quality young fish and feed, adjusting fish breeding structure, strengthening prevention of fish diseases, establishing fishery association, enhancing the ability to guard against disasters and mitigate their damages and providing tailor-made training.
